{
  "video_id": "fi8CYv9Dcr0",
  "title": "Toby Eccles: Invest in social change",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12397.0,
      "end_time": 15957.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here today to talk about social change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15957.0,
      "end_time": 19240.0,
      "text": "not a new therapy or a new intervention"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19240.0,
      "end_time": 21956.0,
      "text": "or a new way of working with kids or something like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21957.0,
      "end_time": 24902.0,
      "text": "but a new business model for social change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24902.0,
      "end_time": 27809.0,
      "text": "a new way of tackling the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27809.0,
      "end_time": 31983.0,
      "text": "In Britain, 63 percent of all men"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31983.0,
      "end_time": 35460.0,
      "text": "who come out of short sentences from prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35460.0,
      "end_time": 37567.0,
      "text": "re-offend again within a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37567.0,
      "end_time": 40185.0,
      "text": "Now how many previous offenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40185.0,
      "end_time": 42568.0,
      "text": "do you think they have on average"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42568.0,
      "end_time": 45153.0,
      "text": "managed to commit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45153.0,
      "end_time": 47301.0,
      "text": "Forty-three."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47301.0,
      "end_time": 50964.0,
      "text": "And how many previous times do you think they&#39;ve been in prison?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50964.0,
      "end_time": 52150.0,
      "text": "Seven."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52151.0,
      "end_time": 54965.0,
      "text": "So we went to talk to the Ministry of Justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54965.0,
      "end_time": 56853.0,
      "text": "and we said to the Ministry of Justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56853.0,
      "end_time": 59205.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s it worth to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59205.0,
      "end_time": 61382.0,
      "text": "if fewer of these guys re-offend?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61382.0,
      "end_time": 63550.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s got to be worth something, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63551.0,
      "end_time": 65378.0,
      "text": "I mean, there&#39;s prison costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65378.0,
      "end_time": 68906.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s police costs, there&#39;s court costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68906.0,
      "end_time": 71638.0,
      "text": "all these things that you&#39;re spending money on"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71638.0,
      "end_time": 74151.0,
      "text": "to deal with these guys. What&#39;s it worth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74151.0,
      "end_time": 77146.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, we care about the social value."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77146.0,
      "end_time": 80432.0,
      "text": "Social Finance, the organization I helped set up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80432.0,
      "end_time": 82675.0,
      "text": "cares about social stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82675.0,
      "end_time": 85717.0,
      "text": "But we wanted to make the economic case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85717.0,
      "end_time": 87495.0,
      "text": "because if we could make the economic case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87495.0,
      "end_time": 90516.0,
      "text": "then the value of doing this  would be completely compelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90516.0,
      "end_time": 93351.0,
      "text": "And if we can agree on both a value"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93351.0,
      "end_time": 95688.0,
      "text": "and a way of measuring whether we&#39;ve been"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95688.0,
      "end_time": 98860.0,
      "text": "successful at reducing that re-offending,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98860.0,
      "end_time": 100570.0,
      "text": "then we can do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100570.0,
      "end_time": 102620.0,
      "text": "we think rather interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102620.0,
      "end_time": 106544.0,
      "text": "The idea is called the social impact bond."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106544.0,
      "end_time": 108920.0,
      "text": "Now, the social impact bond is simply saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108921.0,
      "end_time": 110560.0,
      "text": "if we can get the government to agree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110560.0,
      "end_time": 113311.0,
      "text": "that we can create a contract where"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113311.0,
      "end_time": 116770.0,
      "text": "they only pay if it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116770.0,
      "end_time": 119939.0,
      "text": "So that means that they can try out new stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119939.0,
      "end_time": 121401.0,
      "text": "without the embarrassment"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121402.0,
      "end_time": 123410.0,
      "text": "of having to pay if it didn&#39;t work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123410.0,
      "end_time": 125820.0,
      "text": "which for still quite a lot of bits of government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125820.0,
      "end_time": 126428.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a serious issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126429.0,
      "end_time": 128240.0,
      "text": "Now, many of you may have noticed"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 128240.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129509.00000000001,
      "text": "there&#39;s a problem at this point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129508.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131724.0,
      "text": "and that is that it takes a long time to measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131724.0,
      "end_time": 134489.0,
      "text": "whether those outcomes have happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 134490.0,
      "end_time": 137706.0,
      "text": "So we have to raise some money."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 137706.0,
      "end_time": 140153.0,
      "text": "We use the contract to raise money"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140153.0,
      "end_time": 142376.0,
      "text": "from socially motivated investors."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 142377.0,
      "end_time": 144731.0,
      "text": "Socially motivated investors:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 144731.0,
      "end_time": 147290.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s an interesting idea, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147290.0,
      "end_time": 149420.0,
      "text": "But actually, there&#39;s a lot of people who,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 149420.0,
      "end_time": 150653.0,
      "text": "if they&#39;re given the chance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 150653.0,
      "end_time": 152535.0,
      "text": "would love to invest in something"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152535.0,
      "end_time": 155298.0,
      "text": "that does social good."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 155298.0,
      "end_time": 157271.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s the opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157271.0,
      "end_time": 159528.0,
      "text": "Do you want to also help government find"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159528.0,
      "end_time": 161964.0,
      "text": "whether there&#39;s a better economic model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161964.0,
      "end_time": 164340.0,
      "text": "not just leaving these guys to come out of prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164340.0,
      "end_time": 167211.0,
      "text": "and waiting till they re-offend and putting them back in again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 167211.0,
      "end_time": 168768.0,
      "text": "but actually working with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168768.0,
      "end_time": 170327.0,
      "text": "to move to a different path"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 170327.0,
      "end_time": 172926.0,
      "text": "to end up with fewer crimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 172926.0,
      "end_time": 174940.0,
      "text": "and fewer victims?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 174941.0,
      "end_time": 177452.0,
      "text": "So we find some investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177452.0,
      "end_time": 179822.0,
      "text": "and they pay for a set of services,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179822.0,
      "end_time": 182870.0,
      "text": "and if those services are successful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 182870.0,
      "end_time": 184579.0,
      "text": "then they improve outcomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184580.0,
      "end_time": 187221.0,
      "text": "and with those measured reductions in re-offending,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187221.0,
      "end_time": 188296.0,
      "text": "government saves money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 188296.0,
      "end_time": 189833.0,
      "text": "and with those savings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 189833.0,
      "end_time": 192287.0,
      "text": "they can pay outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 192287.0,
      "end_time": 194463.0,
      "text": "And the investors do not just get their money back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 194463.0,
      "end_time": 196471.0,
      "text": "but they make a return."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 196471.0,
      "end_time": 198912.0,
      "text": "So in March 2010, we signed"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 198912.0,
      "end_time": 200932.0,
      "text": "the first social impact bond"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 200932.0,
      "end_time": 202759.0,
      "text": "with the Ministry of Justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 202759.0,
      "end_time": 204796.0,
      "text": "around Peterborough Prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 204796.0,
      "end_time": 207820.0,
      "text": "It was to work with 3,000 offenders"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 207820.0,
      "end_time": 210748.0,
      "text": "split into three cohorts of 1,000 each."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 210748.0,
      "end_time": 212737.0,
      "text": "Now, each of those cohorts"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 212737.0,
      "end_time": 214567.0,
      "text": "would get measured over the two years"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214568.0,
      "end_time": 215770.0,
      "text": "that they were coming out of prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 215770.0,
      "end_time": 217825.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve got to have a year to commit their crimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 217825.0,
      "end_time": 220369.0,
      "text": "six months to get through the court system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 220370.0,
      "end_time": 222765.0,
      "text": "and then they would be compared to a group"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 222765.0,
      "end_time": 224833.0,
      "text": "taken from the police national computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 224833.0,
      "end_time": 226660.0,
      "text": "as similar as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 226660.0,
      "end_time": 228194.0,
      "text": "and we would get paid"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 228194.0,
      "end_time": 230982.0,
      "text": "providing we achieved a hurdle rate of 10-percent reduction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 230983.0,
      "end_time": 234541.0,
      "text": "for every conviction event that didn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 234541.0,
      "end_time": 238180.0,
      "text": "So we get paid for crimes saved."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 238180.0,
      "end_time": 242122.0,
      "text": "Now if we achieved that 10-percent reduction"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 242122.0,
      "end_time": 243807.0,
      "text": "across all three cohorts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 243807.0,
      "end_time": 246946.0,
      "text": "then the investors get a seven and a half percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 246947.0,
      "end_time": 249900.0,
      "text": "annualized return on their investment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 249900.0,
      "end_time": 250630.0,
      "text": "and if we do better than that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 250630.0,
      "end_time": 252226.0,
      "text": "they can get up to 13 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 252226.0,
      "end_time": 254759.0,
      "text": "annualized return on their investment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254759.0,
      "end_time": 256877.0,
      "text": "which is okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 256877.0,
      "end_time": 260850.0,
      "text": "So everyone wins here, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 260839.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262799.0,
      "text": "The Ministry of Justice can try out a new program"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 262800.0,
      "end_time": 265243.0,
      "text": "and they only pay if it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 265243.0,
      "end_time": 267655.0,
      "text": "Investors get two opportunities:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 267655.0,
      "end_time": 270710.0,
      "text": "for the first time, they can invest in social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 270711.0,
      "end_time": 272742.0,
      "text": "Also, they make a reasonable return,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 272742.0,
      "end_time": 274915.0,
      "text": "and they also know that"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 274915.0,
      "end_time": 277187.0,
      "text": "first investors in these kinds of things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 277187.0,
      "end_time": 278844.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re going to have to believers."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 278844.0,
      "end_time": 280947.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to have to care in the social program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 280947.0,
      "end_time": 282939.0,
      "text": "but if this builds a track record"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 282939.0,
      "end_time": 284387.0,
      "text": "over five or 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 284387.0,
      "end_time": 286451.0,
      "text": "then you can widen that investor community"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 286451.0,
      "end_time": 288907.0,
      "text": "as more people have confidence in the product."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 288907.0,
      "end_time": 291940.0,
      "text": "The service providers, well, for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 291950.0,
      "end_time": 293954.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve got an opportunity to provide services"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 293954.0,
      "end_time": 296181.0,
      "text": "and grow the evidence for what they&#39;re doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 296181.0,
      "end_time": 298741.0,
      "text": "in a really constructive way and learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 298741.0,
      "end_time": 300563.0,
      "text": "and demonstrate the value of what they&#39;re doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 300563.0,
      "end_time": 302582.0,
      "text": "over five or six years, not just one or two"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 302582.0,
      "end_time": 304423.0,
      "text": "as often happens at the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 304423.0,
      "end_time": 307901.0,
      "text": "Society wins: fewer crimes, fewer victims."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 307901.0,
      "end_time": 310727.0,
      "text": "Now, the offenders, they also benefit."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 310727.0,
      "end_time": 312157.0,
      "text": "Instead of just coming out of the prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 312157.0,
      "end_time": 314800.0,
      "text": "with 46 pounds in their pocket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 314810.0,
      "end_time": 315580.0,
      "text": "half of them not knowing where they&#39;re spending"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 315580.0,
      "end_time": 317717.0,
      "text": "their first night out of jail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 317718.0,
      "end_time": 320637.0,
      "text": "actually, someone meets them in prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 320637.0,
      "end_time": 322501.0,
      "text": "learns about their issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 322501.0,
      "end_time": 324419.0,
      "text": "meets them at the gate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 324420.0,
      "end_time": 327173.0,
      "text": "takes them through to somewhere to stay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 327173.0,
      "end_time": 329591.0,
      "text": "connects them to benefits, connects them to employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 329591.0,
      "end_time": 331659.0,
      "text": "drug rehabilitation, mental health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 331659.0,
      "end_time": 333389.0,
      "text": "whatever&#39;s needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 333389.0,
      "end_time": 336680.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s think of another example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 336680.0,
      "end_time": 337957.0,
      "text": "working with children in care."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 337958.0,
      "end_time": 339582.0,
      "text": "Social impact bonds work great"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 339582.0,
      "end_time": 342243.0,
      "text": "for any area where there is at the moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 342243.0,
      "end_time": 344642.0,
      "text": "very expensive provision that produces"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 344642.0,
      "end_time": 346216.0,
      "text": "poor outcomes for people."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 346216.0,
      "end_time": 348130.0,
      "text": "So children in the state care"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 348130.0,
      "end_time": 350565.0,
      "text": "tend to do very badly."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 350565.0,
      "end_time": 354490.0,
      "text": "Only 13 percent achieve a reasonable level"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 354490.0,
      "end_time": 357389.0,
      "text": "of five GCSEs at 16,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 357389.0,
      "end_time": 359859.0,
      "text": "against 58 percent of the wider population."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 359859.0,
      "end_time": 363518.0,
      "text": "More troublingly, 27 percent of offenders in prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 363518.0,
      "end_time": 365558.0,
      "text": "have spent some time in care."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 365559.0,
      "end_time": 366851.0,
      "text": "And even more worryingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 366851.0,
      "end_time": 368823.0,
      "text": "and this is a Home Office statistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 368823.0,
      "end_time": 370722.0,
      "text": "70 percent of prostitutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 370723.0,
      "end_time": 372907.0,
      "text": "have spent some time in care."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 372907.0,
      "end_time": 375907.0,
      "text": "The state is not a great parent."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 375907.0,
      "end_time": 378732.0,
      "text": "But there are great programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 378732.0,
      "end_time": 381744.0,
      "text": "for adolescents who are on the edge of care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 381744.0,
      "end_time": 383620.0,
      "text": "and 30 percent of kids going into care"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 383620.0,
      "end_time": 385279.0,
      "text": "are adolescents."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 385279.0,
      "end_time": 388119.0,
      "text": "So we set up a program with Essex County Council"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 388119.0,
      "end_time": 391765.0,
      "text": "to test out intensive family therapeutic support"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 391765.0,
      "end_time": 394805.0,
      "text": "for those families with adolescents"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 394805.0,
      "end_time": 396376.0,
      "text": "on the edge of the care system."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 396376.0,
      "end_time": 399162.0,
      "text": "Essex only pays in the event"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 399162.0,
      "end_time": 401943.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s saving them care costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 401944.0,
      "end_time": 404708.0,
      "text": "Investors have put in 3.1 million pounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 404708.0,
      "end_time": 406966.0,
      "text": "That program started last month."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 406966.0,
      "end_time": 409290.0,
      "text": "Others, around homelessness in London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 409290.0,
      "end_time": 413170.0,
      "text": "around youth and employment and education"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 413170.0,
      "end_time": 414537.0,
      "text": "elsewhere in the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 414537.0,
      "end_time": 417892.0,
      "text": "There are now 13 social impact bonds in Britain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 417892.0,
      "end_time": 420367.0,
      "text": "and amazing levels of interest in this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 420367.0,
      "end_time": 421890.0,
      "text": "all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 421890.0,
      "end_time": 424604.0,
      "text": "So David Cameron&#39;s put 20 million pounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 424605.0,
      "end_time": 427855.0,
      "text": "into a social outcomes fund to support this idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 427855.0,
      "end_time": 431350.0,
      "text": "Obama has suggested 300 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 431350.0,
      "end_time": 434568.0,
      "text": "in the U.S. budget for these kinds of ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 434568.0,
      "end_time": 436253.0,
      "text": "and structures to move it forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 436254.0,
      "end_time": 437745.0,
      "text": "and a lot of other countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 437745.0,
      "end_time": 439962.0,
      "text": "are demonstrating considerable interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 439962.0,
      "end_time": 442180.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s caused this excitement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 442180.0,
      "end_time": 444537.0,
      "text": "Why is this so different for people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 444537.0,
      "end_time": 447290.0,
      "text": "Well, the first piece, which we&#39;ve talked about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 447290.0,
      "end_time": 448247.0,
      "text": "is innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 448247.0,
      "end_time": 451445.0,
      "text": "It enables testing of new ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 451445.0,
      "end_time": 455380.0,
      "text": "in a way that&#39;s less difficult for everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 455380.0,
      "end_time": 457674.0,
      "text": "The second piece it brings is rigor."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 457674.0,
      "end_time": 460967.0,
      "text": "By working to outcomes, people really have to test"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 460967.0,
      "end_time": 464836.0,
      "text": "and bring data into the situation that one&#39;s dealing with."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 464845.0,
      "end_time": 467338.0,
      "text": "So taking Peterborough as an example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 467338.0,
      "end_time": 469561.0,
      "text": "we add case management"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 469561.0,
      "end_time": 472217.0,
      "text": "across all of the different organizations that we&#39;re working with"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 472217.0,
      "end_time": 473502.0,
      "text": "so they know"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 473502.0,
      "end_time": 475651.0,
      "text": "what actually has been done with different prisoners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 475651.0,
      "end_time": 477720.0,
      "text": "and at the same time they learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 477720.0,
      "end_time": 480146.0,
      "text": "from the Ministry of Justice, and we learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 480146.0,
      "end_time": 481881.0,
      "text": "because we pushed for the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 481881.0,
      "end_time": 484870.0,
      "text": "what actually happens, whether they get re-arrested or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 484880.0,
      "end_time": 487376.0,
      "text": "And we learn and adapt the program accordingly."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 487376.0,
      "end_time": 490313.0,
      "text": "And this leads to the third element, which is new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 490313.0,
      "end_time": 492414.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s flexibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 492415.0,
      "end_time": 495528.0,
      "text": "Because normal contracting for things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 495528.0,
      "end_time": 497589.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;re spending government money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 497589.0,
      "end_time": 500100.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re spending our money, tax money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 500100.0,
      "end_time": 502797.0,
      "text": "and the people who are in charge  of that are very aware of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 502797.0,
      "end_time": 506647.0,
      "text": "so the temptation is to control exactly how you spend it."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 506647.0,
      "end_time": 509700.0,
      "text": "Now any entrepreneur in the room knows"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 509700.0,
      "end_time": 511796.0,
      "text": "that version 1.0, the business plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 511797.0,
      "end_time": 514644.0,
      "text": "is not the one that generally works."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 514644.0,
      "end_time": 516947.0,
      "text": "So when you&#39;re trying to do something like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 516947.0,
      "end_time": 519640.0,
      "text": "you need the flexibility to adapt the program."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 519640.0,
      "end_time": 522352.0,
      "text": "And again, in Peterborough, we started off"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 522352.0,
      "end_time": 526509.0,
      "text": "with a program, but we also collected data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 526509.0,
      "end_time": 528386.0,
      "text": "and over the period of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 528386.0,
      "end_time": 530584.0,
      "text": "we nuanced and changed that program"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 530584.0,
      "end_time": 533204.0,
      "text": "to add a range of other elements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 533204.0,
      "end_time": 534968.0,
      "text": "so that the service adapts"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 534969.0,
      "end_time": 537470.0,
      "text": "and we meet the needs of the long term"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 537470.0,
      "end_time": 539534.0,
      "text": "as well as the short term:"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 539534.0,
      "end_time": 542643.0,
      "text": "greater engagement from the prisoners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 542643.0,
      "end_time": 545422.0,
      "text": "longer-term engagement as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 545422.0,
      "end_time": 547958.0,
      "text": "The last element is partnership."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 547958.0,
      "end_time": 551135.0,
      "text": "There is, at the moment, a stale  debate going on very often:"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 551135.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "state&#39;s better, public sector&#39;s better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 556771.0,
      "text": "private sector&#39;s better, social sector&#39;s better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 556771.0,
      "end_time": 558439.0,
      "text": "for a lot of these programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 558439.0,
      "end_time": 560420.0,
      "text": "Actually, for creating social change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 560421.0,
      "end_time": 562160.0,
      "text": "we need to bring in the expertise"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 562160.0,
      "end_time": 563856.0,
      "text": "from all of those parties"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 563856.0,
      "end_time": 565444.0,
      "text": "in order to make this work."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 565444.0,
      "end_time": 567487.0,
      "text": "And this creates a structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 567487.0,
      "end_time": 569462.0,
      "text": "through which they can combine."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 569462.0,
      "end_time": 571394.0,
      "text": "So where does this leave us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 571394.0,
      "end_time": 573228.0,
      "text": "This leaves us with a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 573228.0,
      "end_time": 576214.0,
      "text": "that people can invest in social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 576215.0,
      "end_time": 579202.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve met thousands, possibly millions of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 579202.0,
      "end_time": 581635.0,
      "text": "who want the opportunity to invest in social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 581635.0,
      "end_time": 584724.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve met champions all over the public sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 584724.0,
      "end_time": 587139.0,
      "text": "keen to make these kinds of differences."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 587139.0,
      "end_time": 588924.0,
      "text": "With this kind of model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 588924.0,
      "end_time": 590860.0,
      "text": "we can help bring them together."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 590860.0,
      "end_time": 592822.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 592822.0,
      "end_time": 597220.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}